title: Ebro In The Morning - Business Disaster Line
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/10.  

Ebro tells us who played themselves (16:41), and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12:30, & 1:01:00). The Crew opens up the Business Disaster Line (43:00) and gives some Guru-like advice (52:30)
